						               													<description>In Test of Faith expansion you will employ hersirs, longships, catapults, and countryside brigands against your foes. You will find mountainous passes on the roads of the land, and churches where you can take refuge.  Each of these five additions provides its own path to accumulating victory points which you can use in concentration or dabble in to supplement your strategy.  At the same time each avenue hinders your rivals in its own fashion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;NEW TILE - PASS is a hex side terrain feature placed across from an empty side, a road side, a mountain side, or another pass.  An unblocked pass side is transited like a road side.  A pass side gives you a church action with which you may construct a church in a town.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion also includes SOLO MODE for new terrain tiles and the all-new TEAM vs. TEAM MODE. With these modules, you will be able to play the game alone and create a team with your friend and face the team of your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
